  "original_title": "\u0b86\u0b95\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b89\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Increase in foreign postal service charges from August",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Posts has informed that the Department of Posts has decided to increase the service charges for foreign posts from August 1.",
        "Ranjith Ariyaratne, Postmaster General of the Department of Posts, commented in this regard,",
        "In this case, the acceptance of postal items to the countries of USA, Netherlands, Israel and Russia has been stopped.",
        "The Postmaster General also said that this decision has been taken due to the current fuel crisis which has limited and suspended flight services to Sri Lanka."
      ],
